# Installation
1 - create a folder in your computer and copy-paste the content of the VagrantFile in a new VagrantFile
2 - vagrant up
3 - vagrant ssh
4 - git clone this repo
5 - execute ./install
6 - quit your vm and come back
7 - execute the file ./make_sure, to be sure everything was install
8 - You can start

# To connect to postgresql ->
sudo -i -u postgres # switch to the user postgres
psql #open postgres

# For expressJS and ReactJS
npm init, at the time to install all dependencies with the package.json
